<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 18:15:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>游泳：中国终结美国对男子4×100米混合泳接力的统治</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/swimming-china-end-us-reign-over-mens-4x100-medley-relay-2024-08-04/</link><description>周日，美国队在男子 4x100 米混合泳比赛中连续 64 年不败的纪录在巴黎奥运会上结束，中国队在拉德芳斯体育馆横扫对手，取得了令人震惊的胜利。</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 17:29:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/swimming-china-end-us-reign-over-mens-4x100-medley-relay-2024-08-04/</guid></item><item><title>羽毛球：台湾选手李、王卫冕男双金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/badminton-taiwans-lee-wang-beat-china-win-mens-doubles-gold-2024-08-04/</link><description>周日，台湾选手李扬/王齐麟在拉夏贝尔体育馆举行的一场扣人心弦的决赛中以21-17 18-21 21-19击败中国选手梁伟铿/王昶，卫冕奥运会羽毛球男双冠军。</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 15:53:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/badminton-taiwans-lee-wang-beat-china-win-mens-doubles-gold-2024-08-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国队凭借刘洋扣环夺得期待已久的金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/gymnastics-china-take-one-two-rings-with-liu-retaining-title-2024-08-04/</link><description>周日，刘洋在吊环决赛中大展拳脚，成功卫冕奥运冠军，为中国队在巴黎奥运会上赢得了期待已久的首枚体操金牌。</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 14:07:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/gymnastics-china-take-one-two-rings-with-liu-retaining-title-2024-08-04/</guid></item><item><title>乒乓球：中国范冰冰夺得男单金牌，法国小将勒布伦获得铜牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/table-tennis-chinas-fan-wins-table-tennis-gold-mens-singles-swede-moregard-2024-08-04/</link><description>中国选手范振东周日在奥运会男子乒乓球单打决赛中击败瑞典选手特鲁斯·莫加德，弥补了三年前在东京错失的金牌。</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 13:30:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/table-tennis-chinas-fan-wins-table-tennis-gold-mens-singles-swede-moregard-2024-08-04/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜表示俄罗斯普京就洪水破坏提供了人道主义援助</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-says-russias-putin-offered-humanitarian-aid-over-flood-damage-2024-08-03/</link><description>大雨袭击了朝鲜西北部地区，4000多所房屋被淹，约5000名居民被隔离</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 22:35:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-says-russias-putin-offered-humanitarian-aid-over-flood-damage-2024-08-03/</guid></item><item><title>网球：郑智击败维克奇为中国队夺得历史性金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/tennis-zheng-beats-vekic-win-historic-gold-china-2024-08-03/</link><description>郑沁文在周六紧张的决赛中以6-2 6-3击败克罗地亚选手唐娜·维克奇，成为首位获得奥运会网球单打金牌的中国选手。</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 16:41:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/tennis-zheng-beats-vekic-win-historic-gold-china-2024-08-03/</guid></item><item><title>乒乓球：中国选手陈再次击败队友孙卫冕女单冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-chinas-chen-beats-teammate-sun-again-defend-womens-singles-title-2024-08-03/</link><description>周六，中国卫冕冠军陈梦在巴黎奥运会上以4比2击败队友孙颖莎，夺得乒乓球女单金牌，就像她在东京奥运会上取得的成绩一样，历史重演。</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 15:01:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-chinas-chen-beats-teammate-sun-again-defend-womens-singles-title-2024-08-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国西南地区洪水、泥石流造成2人死亡，房屋、桥梁被毁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/floods-mudslides-kill-2-southwest-china-destroy-homes-bridge-2024-08-03/</link><description>据官方媒体周六报道，周六，洪水和泥石流摧毁了中国西南省份四川省的村庄房屋和部分高速公路，两起事件造成至少两人死亡、17 人失踪。</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 06:30:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/floods-mudslides-kill-2-southwest-china-destroy-homes-bridge-2024-08-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国就军舰进入台海向加拿大提出投诉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-filed-complaints-with-canada-over-warship-taiwan-strait-2024-08-02/</link><description>中国国防部周五表示，加拿大军舰穿越台湾海峡后，中国已通过军事和外交渠道向加拿大提出投诉。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 10:58:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-filed-complaints-with-canada-over-warship-taiwan-strait-2024-08-02/</guid></item><item><title>酷热席卷华东地区，杭州、上海陷入困境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hangzhou-shanghai-broil-extreme-heat-engulfs-eastern-china-2024-08-02/</link><description>中国东部沿海的大城市正面临又一轮酷暑，周五气温徘徊在 40 摄氏度（104 华氏度）左右，预计下周将持续持续极端气温。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 10:33:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hangzhou-shanghai-broil-extreme-heat-engulfs-eastern-china-2024-08-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国大学开设首个婚姻相关学位课程</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-university-announces-first-marriage-related-degree-course-2024-08-02/</link><description>中国民政大学宣布了一个新的本科婚姻课程，以发展与婚姻相关的产业和文化，此举引起了社交媒体用户的嘲笑，他们质疑在结婚率下降的情况下开设此类课程的必要性。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 08:27:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-university-announces-first-marriage-related-degree-course-2024-08-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国救援人员在致命洪水后竞相寻找失踪的密封堤坝</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/rescuers-china-race-find-missing-seal-dykes-after-devastating-floods-2024-08-02/</link><description>今年最强台风席卷湖南省一周后，中国的救援人员于周五紧急寻找数十名失踪人员，同时紧急救援人员也忙于封堵汹涌河流上决口的堤坝。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 06:25:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/rescuers-china-race-find-missing-seal-dykes-after-devastating-floods-2024-08-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行顾问呼吁加大刺激力度，实现通胀目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-central-bank-adviser-calls-greater-stimulus-inflation-goal-2024-08-02/</link><description>一位央行政策顾问在周五的讲话中表示，中国应加大财政刺激力度以刺激经济增长，并设定坚定的通胀目标，以防止国家陷入“低通胀陷阱”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 05:51:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-central-bank-adviser-calls-greater-stimulus-inflation-goal-2024-08-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国缓慢复苏令全球企业增长前景黯淡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-stuttering-recovery-darkens-global-corporate-growth-outlook-2024-08-02/</link><description>全球汉堡连锁店和汽车制造商越来越感受到世界第二大经济体中国复苏乏力的压力，并准备迎接未来的坎坷之路。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 04:18:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-stuttering-recovery-darkens-global-corporate-growth-outlook-2024-08-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国官方媒体和网民在潘基文声称“人类不可能”完成100米游泳后团结起来</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/chinas-state-media-netizens-rally-around-pan-after-claims-100m-swim-not-humanly-2024-08-02/</link><description>在包括澳大利亚游泳评论员在内的批评者称潘占乐在100米自由泳中创造世界纪录“不可能”之后，中国官方媒体、运动员和网民纷纷集会支持奥运会游泳冠军潘占乐。</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 03:03:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/chinas-state-media-netizens-rally-around-pan-after-claims-100m-swim-not-humanly-2024-08-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>